embeds.description:
Introduce yourself! Please keep this friendly and SFW.

Tell us a bit about yourself.  Who you are, where you're based, your role in vfx, how you found us.

Feel free to share as much or as little as you wish -- none of this is required.  Here's an example post:

- name; 
- your gig/interest in VFX;
- location; 
- how did you find us?
